Class RequiredValueValidator<V extends RequiredValueValidator<V>>

    public class RequiredValueValidator<V extends RequiredValueValidator<V>>
extends AbstractValidator<V>
    Validates that a value is required. The validation only occurs if a component is shown and enabled.

    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
